Thomas R. JAMES, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2152 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 14, 2017
